title: 146 - Q and Andy
description:
This episode, is special, as Andy graces the podcast for his final official show as co-host. But, instead I'll be interviewing him as he is moving on to some pretty incredible things that I really want to make room for him to share. 

Check out his ongoing work at http://www.andylikeswords.com

Learn more about the VOX Podcast:
